920/0/en/Port-Moresby-Stock-Exchange-POMSoX-Launches-New-Nasdaq-Trading-System.html}}</ref>\n|XPOM\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[List of stock exchanges]]\n\n[[Category:Stock exchanges in Oceania|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of stock exchanges|Oceania]]\n", "text_old": "[[File:Oceania_(orthographic_projection).svg|right|thumb|300px|Oceania]]\nThis is a '''list of active stock exchanges in Oceania'''.\n\n== Stock Exchanges in Oceania ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Economy\n!Exchange\n!Location\n!Founded\n!Listings\n!Link\n!Technology\n!Operating MIC\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |{{flagicon|Australia}} [[Australia]]\n|[[APTEX]]\n|[[Sydney]]\n|2008\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Asia Pacific Stock Exchange]]\n|[[Sydney]]\n|1997\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Australian Securities Exchange]]\n|[[Sydney]]\n|1987\n|\n|[http://www.asx.com.au/ ASX]\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Chi-X Australia]]\n|[[Sydney]]\n|\n|\n| [https://www.chi-x.com.au/ CXA]\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[National Stock Exchange of Australia]]\n|[[Sydney]]\n|1937\n|\n| [https://www.nsx.com.au/ NSX]\n| Nasdaq X-stream<ref>{{cite web |title=Exchange technology operates using the world leading FinTech Nasdaq X-Stream trading platform |url=https://www.nsx.com.au/about/our-business/}}</ref>\n|XNEC\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Fiji}} [[Fiji]]\n|[[South Pacific Stock Exchange]]\n|[[Suva]]\n|1971\n|\n|[http://www.spse.com.fj/ SPX]\n|\n|XSPS\n|-\n|{{flagicon|New Zealand}} [[New Zealand]]\n|[[New Zealand Exchange]]\n|[[Wellington]]\n|2002\n|\n| [https://www.nzx.com/ NZX]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Papua New Guinea}} [[Papua New Guinea]]\n|[[PNGX Markets Limited]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Port Moresby Stock Exchange Changes NameTo PNGX Markets Limited |url=https://www.businessadvantagepng.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/PNGX_announcement.pdf}}</ref>\n|[[Port Moresby]]\n|1999\n|\n|[http://www.pngx.com.pg/ PNGX]\n|Nasdaq Matching Engine<ref>{{cite web |title=Port Moresby Stock Exchange (POMSoX) Launches New Nasdaq Trading System |url=https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2017/11/21/1197920/0/en/Port-M